{"title":"P2 基本不等式应用","date":"2021-09-30T23:47:31.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 1, 2021","L":"10/01/2021","MM-DD":"10-01"},"link":"posts/50bec22a","tags":["最值"],"categories":["基本不等式"],"updated":"2021-10-01T09:23:17.229Z","content":"<div class=\"admonition note\"><p class=\"admonition-title\">P2\n</p><p>已知$ x&gt;0,y&gt;0;x+2y=1 $，求$ x^{2}+4y^{2}+2xy $的最小值.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"admonition note\"><p class=\"admonition-title\">P3\n</p><p>已知$ a&gt;0,b&gt;0;a+2b=1 $，求$ \\frac{b^{2}+a+1}{ab}  $ 的最小值.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"admonition note\"><p class=\"admonition-title\">P4\n</p><p>已知$ x&gt;0,y&gt;0;xy^{2}(x+y)=4 $，求$ 2x+y $的最小值.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"admonition note\"><p class=\"admonition-title\">P5\n</p><p>已知$ x,y\\ge 0;x^{2}+4y^{2}+4xy+4x^{2}y^{2}=32 $，求$ \\sqrt{7} (x+2y)+2xy $的最大值.</p>\n</div>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>","next":{"title":"P1 小题","link":"posts/aabc4f91"},"plink":"https://win-keep199.github.io/posts/50bec22a/"}